## 📡 C2 INTERACTION MENU COMMANDS
- background / bg      : Return to main CLI while keeping the session active.
- load <path>          : Silently inject a script or binary into target RAM.
- auto_root            : Attempt automated privilege escalation to root.
- dump_sms / calls     : Exfiltrate SMS inbox or call logs.
- dump_wifi / chrome   : Extract WiFi PSKs, browser cookies, and logins.
- dump_google_passwords: Targeted GMS and System credential extraction.
- find_cookies / pass  : Recursive search for cookie and password stores.
- get_location         : Extract last known GPS coordinates.
- upload / download    : Securely transfer files via the encrypted tunnel.
- clear                : Clear the terminal screen.
- help / ?             : Display the detailed interaction help menu.

